snippet.title: Swing Around With Your Extendable Arms In This Retro 3D Platformer | JeliWave (Demo)
snippet.description:
JeliWave is a retro 3d platformer where you navigate your way through various stages with your extendable arms.

Like, Comment, and Subscribe if you like the video!

"JeliWave" by Team Hartlock
